.6672V19.3332H27.6666C28.2187 19.3333 28.6665 19.7811 28.6666 20.3332C28.6666 20.8854 28.2188 21.3331 27.6666 21.3332H23.9996V25.0002C23.9996 25.5524 23.5519 26.0002 22.9996 26.0002C22.4474 26.0001 21.9996 25.5524 21.9996 25.0002V21.3332H18.3326C17.7805 21.333 17.3326 20.8853 17.3326 20.3332C17.3328 19.7812 17.7806 19.3334 18.3326 19.3332H21.9996V15.6672C21.9996 15.1149 22.4474 14.6672 22.9996 14.6672ZM17.8863 0.105648C18.3802 -0.141093 18.9812 0.0590708 19.2281 0.552914L22.2848 6.66717L25.2926 6.66717C25.6819 6.66716 26.0236 6.66658 26.3043 6.68573C26.5977 6.70574 26.912 6.75043 27.2193 6.88592C27.7362 7.11384 28.1316 7.46314 28.3785 7.92205C28.616 8.3636 28.6728 8.82745 28.6656 9.22381C28.6585 9.61744 28.5861 10.0022 28.5143 10.3234C28.4704 10.5195 28.4372 10.6548 28.4068 10.7765C28.3745 10.9061 28.3461 11.0211 28.3131 11.1779C28.2048 11.691 27.8583 12.1058 27.4039 12.3215C27.1212 12.4556 26.894 12.6553 26.7369 12.8898C26.4296 13.3487 25.8081 13.4715 25.3492 13.1642C24.8906 12.8569 24.7676 12.2353 25.0748 11.7765C25.4048 11.2839 25.8578 10.8754 26.3951 10.59C26.4214 10.477 26.4528 10.3484 26.482 10.2277C26.5146 10.0934 26.5448 10.3484 26.482 10.2277C26.5146 10.0934 26.5448 9.96868 26.5631 9.8869C26.6259 9.60598 26.6632 9.3774 26.6666 9.18768C26.67 9.00048 26.6385 8.90966 26.6168 8.86932C26.6043 8.84614 26.5682 8.785 26.4117 8.716C26.4063 8.71374 26.3547 8.69355 26.1686 8.68084C25.9642 8.6669 25.6916 8.66717 25.2613 8.66717L13.6666 8.66717C13.1144 8.66717 12.6668 8.21928 12.6666 7.66717C12.6666 7.11489 13.1143 6.66717 13.6666 6.66717L20.0484 6.66717L17.4391 1.44745C17.1921 0.953475 17.3924 0.35263 17.8863 0.105648Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>' %}
